---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Automation for Nuts and Dried Fruit Manufacturers — Formic"
  description="Too much overtime, not enough people. Dried fruit and nut production takes time, precision, and people. Formic makes it easy. Robotic palletizing and case packing under one monthly fee."
  ogTitle="Automation for Nuts and Dried Fruit Manufacturers — Formic"
  ogDescription="Fully managed robotic palletizing and case packing for nuts and dried fruit manufacturers. No CapEx, deployed in weeks."
>
  <link rel="canonical" href="https://formic.co/results/nuts-and-dried-fruit" slot="head" />
  <style is:global slot="head">
    .ind-yt-wrap{position:relative;width:100%;max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;aspect-ratio:16/9;background:#000;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08)}
    .ind-yt-wrap iframe{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;border:0}
    .ind-qbox{background:var(--white);padding:34px 32px;border-left:3px solid var(--orange);margin:18px 0 22px}
    .ind-qbox blockquote{font-family:var(--sans);font-size:19px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.5;color:var(--black);margin:0 0 14px;letter-spacing:-.005em}
    .ind-qbox .ind-qattr{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mgrey)}
  </style>

<div class="detail-bc">
  <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">/</span><a href="/results">Results</a><span class="sep">/</span>Nuts &amp; Dried Fruit
</div>

<section class="detail-hero">
  <div class="si">
    <div class="slabel" style="color:var(--orange)">Industry · Nuts &amp; Dried Fruit</div>
    <h1>Automation for nuts <br><em>and dried fruit manufacturers</em>.</h1>
    <p class="lede">Too much overtime, not enough people. Downtime that drives you nuts. Dried fruit and nut production takes time, precision, and people. We make it easy.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="detail-video wide">
    <div class="detail-video-frame">
      <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="/stories/georgia-nut/1642517481-screen-shot-2022-01-14-at-2-49-19-pm.png">
        <source src="/Formic-Header.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      </video>
      <span class="dv-cap">Automate NOW · nuts &amp; dried fruit</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block white">
  <div class="db-grid">
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">$0 CapEx · Deployed in weeks</div>
      <h2>Automate your line. <em>Deploy in weeks</em>.</h2>
      <p>Palletizing and case packing that work from day one. No hiring. No retraining. No headaches. Just consistent output.</p>
      <ul class="feats">
        <li>Cut reliance on temp labor and seasonal hiring spikes</li>
        <li>Pay-for-uptime alignment — Formic gets paid when the line runs</li>
        <li>Process flexibility for varied pack formats and SKU mixes</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/contact/get-a-quote" class="larr">Talk to a nuts &amp; dried fruit automation engineer →</a>
      <p style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;margin:18px 0 0"><a href="/downloads/Formic-Best-Practices-Nuts-Dried-Fruit-Mariani.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color:var(--orange);text-decoration:none;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px">↓ Download the nuts &amp; dried fruit best practices guide (PDF)</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/Formic-Casepacker-Plant.jpg" alt="Formic robotic case packer running on a customer line" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Case packing · 24/7</span></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block lgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/stories/georgia-nut/1642517481-screen-shot-2022-01-14-at-2-49-19-pm.png" alt="Georgia Nut palletizing cell — first robot in company history" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Georgia Nut · skin in the game</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">Customer story</div>
      <h2>Georgia Nut drives throughput <em>with automation</em>.</h2>
      <div class="ind-qbox">
        <blockquote>"Formic has some skin in the game, because they're only getting incentivized when the machine is running, not when it's down."</blockquote>
        <div class="ind-qattr">Matt Neuman · Distribution and Packaging Manager, Georgia Nut</div>
      </div>
      <a href="/stories/georgia-nut" class="larr">Read the Georgia Nut story →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dark">
  <div class="si" style="max-width:1280px;margin:0 auto;padding:80px;text-align:center">
    <div class="db-tag" style="justify-content:center">Stop going nuts over temp labor — Automate NOW</div>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--sans);font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,56px);font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-.02em;line-height:1.05;color:var(--white);margin:8px 0 28px">Automate nuts and dried fruit lines — <em style="color:var(--orange);font-style:normal">for $0 in CapEx</em>.</h2>
    <div class="ind-yt-wrap">
      <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/SD0UMnNYR1E" title="Formic Full Service Automation" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen loading="lazy"></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-block dgrey">
  <div class="db-grid flip">
    <div class="db-img"><img src="/articles/automation-in-action-inside-mariani-packing-s-facility-tour-panel-on-why-manufact/1755024817-marianifac_r52_8289.jpg" alt="Mariani Packing facility tour — process flexibility through automation" loading="lazy"/><span class="img-cap">Mariani Packing · process flexibility</span></div>
    <div class="db-text">
      <div class="db-tag">Customer story</div>
      <h2>Mariani Packing increases <em>process flexibility</em>.</h2>
      <div class="ind-qbox" style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border-left-color:var(--orange)">
        <blockquote style="color:var(--white)">"The strongest asset that we have as a company is truly our people. You can have the best automation, the best process technology, but if we don't use it and improve it daily, you won't achieve your goals."</blockquote>
        <div class="ind-qattr" style="color:rgba(240,245,241,.65)">Jesus Ceja · Director, Mariani Packing</div>
      </div>
      <a href="/articles/automation-in-action-inside-mariani-packing-s-facility-tour-panel-on-why-manufact" class="larr">Read more on Mariani Packing →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="detail-cta">
  <h2>Get started with automation<br><em>today</em>.</h2>
  <div class="btn-row">
    <a href="/contact/get-a-quote" class="btn-ctadark">Get a Quote</a>
    <a href="/results" class="btn-ctawh">All Industries</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
